  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Front Seat Back Trim Cover/Pad Removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "If there are components of the SRS airbag system in the vicinity, refer to the work precautions and configuration drawings described for the SRS airbag system before proceeding."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. 12V battery Negative (-) terminal Disconnect",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000910",
          "label": "12V battery Negative (-) terminal Disconnect",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2. Front seat removal",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000792",
          "label": "Front seat removal",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3. Front seat armrest removal (driver side)",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000793",
          "label": "Front seat armrest removal (driver side)",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "4. Remove front seat back trim cover/pad"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "797_3.0_jpn_11581336_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "797_3.0_jpn_11581337_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "For vehicles equipped with side airbags: Remove the hook (A) of the back trim cover from behind the seat cushion. Vehicles equipped with side airbags: Disconnect the coupler clip (B) and harness clip (C)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "797_3.0_jpn_11581338_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "3",
      "text": "For vehicles equipped with side airbags: Pull the side airbag harness (A) out of the seat cushion trim cover (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "797_3.0_jpn_11581339_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "4",
      "text": "For vehicles equipped with side airbags: Pull the side airbag harness (A) through the hole (B) in the seat back trim cover."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "797_3.0_jpn_11581340_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "5",
      "text": "Remove the hook (A) on the underside of the seat back trim cover and pull up the zipper (B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "797_3.0_jpn_11581341_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "6",
      "text": "For vehicles equipped with side airbags: Remove the harness clip (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "797_3.0_jpn_11581342_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "7",
      "text": "For vehicles equipped with side airbags: Remove the nut on the inside of the seat."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "797_3.0_jpn_11581343_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "8",
      "text": "Remove the headrest guide (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "797_3.0_jpn_11581344_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "9",
      "text": "Remove the seat back trim cover/pad (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "5. Side airbag removal (vehicles equipped with side airbags)",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R001642",
          "label": "Side airbag removal (vehicles equipped with side airbags)",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "6. Installation Precautions"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Installation is the reverse of the removal procedure."
    }
  ],
